package.name: Payin7_Payments
package.summary: The official magento plugin of the Payin7 payments service gateway (http://www.payin7.com)
package.description:
Payin7 discovers to your clients the possibility of delaying payment 7 days so they can check their purchase before they pay it or to finance their purchases in easy installments.
If you are a buyer you can effortlessly acquire what you want or even a better item than what you previusly want.
If you are a store you will offer an attractive alternative payment to your customers so they have bigger margen to think about payment.
package.notes:
First release of the extension.
If you are not a customer yet but would like to become one email: info@payin7.com.
Report bugs and issues to: support@payin7.com.
